node.content: ["The border between Victoria and NSW has reopened\u00a0for the first time in months, in changes that will enable \"free travel\" between the country's two most-populous states.", "But it's not all good news, with\u00a0residents in Katherine\u00a0waking up to a snap lockdown after the Northern Territory recorded its first case of community transmission of COVID-19.\u00a0", "Follow all of Friday's COVID-19 news and updates on our live blog."]
